                    <b><ins>MEASURES TO USE EFFICIENT AND SAFE WATER WATER:</ins></b>
                    <p class="text-information">With the above limitations, it is necessary to note in the use of rainwater as follows: Do not collect rainwater at the beginning of the season, you should collect it after a heavy rain for about 15-20 minutes to let the rain wash away the dirt in the air. It is necessary to clean the storage tanks, collecting devices and carefully cover them to avoid the spread of contaminants. In addition, in the use of rainwater for daily life, it is not recommended to using rainwater after collecting or storing it for direct consumption because it will contain harmful substances that cannot be seen by the naked eye, it is necessary to filter the water before putting it into use.</p>
